---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Domov"
description: "Golfové ihrisko GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK, Ivanka pri Nitre. Golfový klub MEANDER — členstvo, cenník, tréning."
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__bg"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <p class="hero__eyebrow">Ivanka pri Nitre · Sezóna 2026</p>
    <h1 class="hero__title">Green<br>Meadows</h1>
    <p class="hero__sub">Golfové ihrisko &amp; GK Meander</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a href="/golfove-ihrisko/" class="btn btn--white">Preskúmajte ihrisko</a>
      <a href="/cennik/" class="btn btn--outline">Cenník 2026</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero__scroll" onclick="document.getElementById('intro').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Scroll</div>
</section>

<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stats-bar__inner container">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat__number">2×</div>
      <div class="stat__label">9-jamkové ihriská</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat__number">250m</div>
      <div class="stat__label">Driving range</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat__number">18€</div>
      <div class="stat__label">Green fee / 9 jamiek</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat__number">150</div>
      <div class="stat__label">Miest v klube</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section" id="intro">
  <div class="intro-card">
    <div class="intro-card__title">Vitajte na golfe v Ivanke pri Nitre</div>
    <p class="intro-card__text">
      9-jamkové golfové ihriská GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK pre všetky hráčske úrovne, tréningové plochy, výuka golfu
      a golfové firemné podujatia. Ihrisko je sídlom Golfového klubu Meander — členovia môžu využívať ihrisko
      počas i mimo hlavnej sezóny už od <strong>250,- EUR</strong>. Celý kurz golfu vrátane voľnej golfovej hry
      môžete získať za <strong>450,- EUR</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.announcements | length %}
<section class="section section--gray">
  <div class="container--sm">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Novinky</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Aktuálne informácie</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="announcements">
      {% for post in collections.announcements | limit(5) %}
      <div class="announcement-card{% if post.data.pinned %} announcement-card--pinned{% endif %}">
        {% if post.data.pinned %}<span class="announcement-card__pin">Pripnuté</span>{% endif %}
        <div class="announcement-card__date">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</div>
        <div class="announcement-card__body">
          <div class="announcement-card__title">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
          <div class="announcement-card__text">{{ post.templateContent | safe }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="section-label">Čo tu nájdete</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Všetko na jednom mieste</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="quicklinks-grid">
      <a href="/golfove-ihrisko/" class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">⛳</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Golfové ihrisko</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Green Meadows &amp; Green Park — 9-jamkové ihriská, driving range, chipping area</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/gk-meander/" class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">🏌</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">GK Meander</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Členstvo, výhody a podmienky vstupu do klubu. NO TEETIME — NO STRESS.</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/cennik/" class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">💶</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Cenník 2026</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Green fee, voučery, otváracie hodiny recepcie</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/info-blok/treningy-zelene-karty/" class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">🎓</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Tréningy &amp; zelené karty</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Kurzy golfu, zelené karty, individuálne tréningy</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/rezervacia/" class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">📅</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Rezervácia tréningu</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Online rezervácia termínu tréningu u nášho PGA trénera</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/kontakt/" class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">📍</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Kontakt</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Adresa, telefón, email a fakturačné údaje</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="holes-section">
  <div class="holes-section__bg"></div>
  <div class="holes-section__content">
    <div class="holes-section__title">Preskúmajte Green Meadows jamku za jamkou</div>
    <div class="holes-list">
      {% for i in range(1, 10) %}
      <a href="/golfove-ihrisko/green-meadows/" class="holes-list__item">{{ i }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <a href="/golfove-ihrisko/green-meadows/" class="btn btn--outline" style="margin-top:3rem;">Detail ihriska</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="video-section">
  <div class="video-section__inner container">
    <div class="video-section__text-col">
      <p class="video-section__label">Video pozvánka</p>
      <h2 class="video-section__title">Pozrite si naše ihrisko</h2>
      <p class="video-section__text">
        Golfové ihrisko GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK leží v krásnej krajine pri Nitre. Príroda, ticho a dobrý golf
        — to je náš recept na dokonalý deň na ihrisku.
      </p>
      <a href="{{ site.youtube }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--outline">Pozrieť na YouTube ↗</a>
    </div>
    <div class="video-section__embed-col">
      <div class="video-section__embed">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dGbBqlSzMEY"
          title="Green Meadows Golf — video pozvánka"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="partners-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="partners-strip__label">Naši partneri &amp; asociácie</div>
    <div class="partners-strip__logos">
      <a href="https://www.kartoma.sk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partners-strip__logo">Kartoma</a>
      <a href="https://www.golfinstitute.sk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partners-strip__logo">Golf Institute</a>
      <a href="https://www.corado.sk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partners-strip__logo">Corado</a>
      <a href="https://www.skg.sk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partners-strip__logo">SKG</a>
      <a href="https://www.pgacz.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partners-strip__logo">PGA of Czech Republic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
